<segment id="1" parent="1001" relname="preparation">Think Like a Businessman</segment>
<segment id="2" parent="1002" relname="preparation">We all need to do to business at some point in life ,</segment>
<segment id="3" parent="1002" relname="joint">whether it 's a small trade or a huge business one .</segment>
<segment id="4" parent="1005" relname="span">It is important to think like a businessman for many reasons</segment>
<segment id="5" parent="4" relname="elaboration">like to avoid fraud ,</segment>
<segment id="6" parent="1006" relname="contrast">earn a little cash ,</segment>
<segment id="7" parent="1007" relname="joint">or stay out of debt ,</segment>
<segment id="8" parent="1007" relname="joint">and this article will teach you how to think like a real businessman !</segment>
<segment id="9" parent="1009" relname="preparation">Steps</segment>
<segment id="10" parent="1009" relname="joint">Do cost benefits analysis of things .</segment>
<segment id="11" parent="1009" relname="joint">this is the basis of most profitable decisions .</segment>
<segment id="12" parent="1013" relname="joint">here you are weighing up what you expect to lose in comparison to what you expect to gain</segment>
<segment id="13" parent="1014" relname="same_unit">and what benefits you will get</segment>
<segment id="14" parent="1014" relname="same_unit">from taking certain pathways .</segment>
<segment id="15" parent="1015" relname="joint">Figure out the usefulness and benefit of products .</segment>
<segment id="16" parent="1016" relname="span">usefulness and benefit of things often transcribe to whether or not the product is sell-able .</segment>
<segment id="17" parent="1018" relname="span">when you analyse things</segment>
<segment id="18" parent="1019" relname="span">look</segment>
<segment id="19" parent="1020" relname="span">to see how much use</segment>
<segment id="20" parent="19" relname="elaboration">it provides .</segment>
<segment id="21" parent="1021" relname="sequence">Have a vision .</segment>
<segment id="22" parent="1023" relname="same_unit">A vision of what you aim to create</segment>
<segment id="23" parent="1024" relname="joint">is what draws people to you</segment>
<segment id="24" parent="1024" relname="joint">and inspires others to your cause .</segment>
<segment id="25" parent="1025" relname="joint">A good vision will gain you many supporters and investors .</segment>
<segment id="26" parent="1027" relname="span">it is useful to look at the visions of others</segment>
<segment id="27" parent="26" relname="purpose">to determine which visions are worthwhile .</segment>
<segment id="28" parent="1028" relname="joint">Value your time .</segment>
<segment id="29" parent="1030" relname="span">Time is something</segment>
<segment id="30" parent="1031" relname="sequence">you never get back</segment>
<segment id="31" parent="1032" relname="same_unit">and valuing it</segment>
<segment id="32" parent="1032" relname="same_unit">makes you spend it well .</segment>
<segment id="33" parent="1034" relname="span">Old age and death creep up on people</segment>
<segment id="34" parent="1035" relname="joint">before they are aware</segment>
<segment id="35" parent="1035" relname="joint">and they live with lots of regrets .</segment>
<segment id="36" parent="1036" relname="joint">managing your time well also makes people respect you .</segment>
<segment id="37" parent="38" relname="attribution">Look to see</segment>
<segment id="38" parent="1038" relname="span">how you can best organise people .</segment>
<segment id="39" parent="1040" relname="span">The organisation of people for a purpose is the fundamental aspect of a company .</segment>
<segment id="40" parent="1042" relname="condition">if you can organise people for a reason</segment>
<segment id="41" parent="1042" relname="joint">you can form a company</segment>
<segment id="42" parent="1042" relname="joint">and begin .</segment>
<segment id="43" parent="1043" relname="sequence">Pay attention to where things are going to waste .</segment>
<segment id="44" parent="1045" relname="span">A sense of wastefulness is paramount</segment>
<segment id="45" parent="1046" relname="span">to reorganising your resources in a way</segment>
<segment id="46" parent="45" relname="elaboration">that is best for you .</segment>
<segment id="47" parent="48" relname="condition">If you have no sense of where things are going to waste</segment>
<segment id="48" parent="1048" relname="span">then you will dwindle accumulated wealth little by little .</segment>
<segment id="49" parent="1050" relname="span">Look at what is going to waste -</segment>
<segment id="50" parent="1051" relname="sequence">energy , time , resources , skills</segment>
<segment id="51" parent="1052" relname="span">and then find ways</segment>
<segment id="52" parent="51" relname="purpose">to use them .</segment>
<segment id="53" parent="1053" relname="sequence">Pay attention to innovative ideas and methods .</segment>
<segment id="54" parent="1055" relname="span">In this way , you develop a means</segment>
<segment id="55" parent="1056" relname="span">to do things in ways</segment>
<segment id="56" parent="55" relname="elaboration">that are more efficient .</segment>
<segment id="57" parent="1057" relname="span">many people have it in their heads</segment>
<segment id="58" parent="1060" relname="span">that the only way</segment>
<segment id="59" parent="58" relname="elaboration">to do things</segment>
<segment id="60" parent="1061" relname="span">is the way</segment>
<segment id="61" parent="60" relname="elaboration">that it has been done for a long time ,</segment>
<segment id="62" parent="1062" relname="joint">however , this is not based in reality</segment>
<segment id="63" parent="1062" relname="joint">and can be very time consuming for little reward .</segment>
<segment id="64" parent="1064" relname="preparation">Tips</segment>
<segment id="65" parent="66" relname="attribution">If you 're not sure</segment>
<segment id="66" parent="1066" relname="span">whether a trade is good or not</segment>
<segment id="67" parent="1067" relname="span">be sure to ask a friend or family member</segment>
<segment id="68" parent="67" relname="purpose">to avoid getting ripped off !</segment>
<segment id="69" parent="1069" relname="preparation">Warnings</segment>
<segment id="70" parent="71" relname="condition">If you are n't careful</segment>
<segment id="71" parent="1070" relname="span">you may lose a lot of cash and/or items !</segment>
<segment id="72" parent="1071" relname="span">Do NOT make illegal trades/business deals !</segment>
<segment id="73" parent="1073" relname="concession">You may not start thinking like one right away ,</segment>
<segment id="74" parent="75" relname="attribution">but remember</segment>
<segment id="75" parent="1073" relname="span">practice makes perfect !</segment>
